sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Gateway / Envoy<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant EPP as Endpoint Picker (EPP)<br/>ext-proc gRPC
    participant Pool as InferencePool<br/>(K8s CRD)
    participant vLLM as Model Server (vLLM)<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>9002/9090 TCP

    Note over Client, vLLM: Standard Inference Flow (Optimized Baseline)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>OpenAI-compatible API
    Gateway->>EPP: ext-proc gRPC<br/>Request headers + body

    Note over EPP: Filter → Score → Pick Pipeline
    EPP->>Pool: Query available endpoints<br/>(label-based discovery)
    Pool-->>EPP: Endpoint list<br/>(ready model server pods)

    Note over EPP: Scoring:<br/>KV cache utilization<br/>Queue depth<br/>Prefix cache affinity<br/>LoRA affinity

    EPP-->>Gateway: Selected endpoint address<br/>(ext-proc response)
    Gateway->>vLLM: Forward request to<br/>selected model server<br/>HTTP/8000
    vLLM-->>Gateway: Streaming response<br/>(SSE / JSON)
    Gateway-->>Client: Response stream

    Note over vLLM, Prom: Metrics Collection (Continuous)
    vLLM->>Prom: Expose metrics<br/>queue_depth, kv_cache_util,<br/>running_requests
    Prom-->>EPP: Poll metrics<br/>(scheduling decisions)

    Note over Client, vLLM: Prefill/Decode Disaggregation Flow

    participant Sidecar as Routing Sidecar<br/>8000/TCP
    participant Prefill as Prefill Worker<br/>8000/TCP
    participant NIXL as NIXL Transfer<br/>5600/TCP RDMA
    participant Decode as Decode Worker<br/>8200/TCP

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions
    Gateway->>EPP: ext-proc gRPC
    Note over EPP: disagg-profile-handler<br/>Selects P & D worker pair
    EPP-->>Gateway: Prefill endpoint + Decode endpoint
    Gateway->>Sidecar: Forward to routing sidecar<br/>HTTP/8000
    Sidecar->>Prefill: Prefill request<br/>(max_tokens=1)<br/>HTTP/8000
    Prefill->>NIXL: KV cache transfer<br/>GPUDirect RDMA<br/>Port 5600
    NIXL->>Decode: KV blocks transferred<br/>NVLink / RoCE / InfiniBand
    Decode-->>Sidecar: Decode response<br/>HTTP/8200
    Sidecar-->>Gateway: Streaming response
    Gateway-->>Client: Response stream

    Note over Client, vLLM: Precise Prefix Cache-Aware Routing

    participant ZMQ as ZMQ Publisher<br/>5556/TCP

    vLLM->>ZMQ: KV cache block events<br/>(block hash, add/remove)
    ZMQ->>EPP: Real-time cache index<br/>updates via ZMQ
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions
    Gateway->>EPP: ext-proc gRPC
    Note over EPP: precise-prefix-cache-scorer<br/>Routes to pod with highest<br/>prefix-block residency
    EPP-->>Gateway: Best-match endpoint
    Gateway->>vLLM: Forward (cache hit)<br/>HTTP/8000
    vLLM-->>Client: Fast response<br/>(prefix cached)
